<p align="center">
<font color="#006400" size="+2"><a name="bio">Biographical</a></font>
</p>

<blockquote>
<table>
<tr>
    <td>Name:</td>    
    <td>Stephen Michael (&quot;Steve&quot;) ERICKSON</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Nationality:</td>
    <td>USA</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Born:</td>    
    <td>20 April 1950</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Awards:</td>
    <td>Samuel Goldwyn Award for fiction, 1972</td>
</tr>
</table>
<br>

<font size="-1">
<ul>
	<li>Attended the University of California at Los Angeles (B.A., 1972; M.A. 1973)
	<li>Arts editor, <i>Los Angeles Weekly</i>, 1989-1991
</ul>
</font>

</blockquote>

